{"prompt": "Design a portfolio for an architect. The site should be minimalist, featuring a lemon chiffon yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Architect Portfolio</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #fefefe;\n            --secondary-color: #fef2e4; /* A lighter, less contrasting shade than lemon chiffon */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --accent-color: #fefae0; /* A subtle lemon chiffon */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--accent-color);\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #fef2e4 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #main-content h2 {\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .project {\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            background: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .project:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n\n        .project img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .project h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            background: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-top: #fef2e4 3px solid;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info {\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>[Architect Name]</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <div id=\"main-content\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Selected Works</h2>\n\n        <div class=\"project\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/800x500/fefae0/333333?text=Project+1+Image\" alt=\"Project 1\">\n            <h3>Project Title One</h3>\n            <p>A brief description of the first architectural project, highlighting its key features and design philosophy.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"project\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/800x500/fefae0/333333?text=Project+2+Image\" alt=\"Project 2\">\n            <h3>Project Title Two</h3>\n            <p>A brief description of the second architectural project, emphasizing innovative solutions and aesthetic appeal.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"project\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/800x500/fefae0/333333?text=Project+3+Image\" alt=\"Project 3\">\n            <h3>Project Title Three</h3>\n            <p>A brief description of the third architectural project, showcasing its impact and context.</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>Get in touch</p>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <p>Email: [your.email@example.com]</p>\n                <p>Phone: [Your Phone Number]</p>\n                <p>Location: [Your City, Country]</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}